prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon slice of cherry pie with big googly eyes and a wide, mischievous grin, holding a single lit birthday candle in one of its flaky crust "hands". The pie slice is dramatically leaning away from a cartoon fork that is swooping in from the side, as if trying to take a bite. The text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script in the center of the card. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting with soft, blended colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds along the edges of the figures.
